ics you must go to &quot;Sephora&quot; on broadway and spring st . it is heaven if you want to sit and try lots of cosmetics then remove them and try more, they have good brand choices and far less expensive than the UK. The staff are very helpfull and there are lots of them to put on make up if and show you how to use the products if you want to, if you preffer to do your own no worries there are lots of full size mirrors and make up brushes around for you to do some DIY.	
